First set variables in 000.source_global_var.sh and set them by:
   source 000.source_global_var.sh

This first step must be run anytime a new session is started to reset variables at any stage of scripts

Change Job name and Output name before running below step if running in slurm
   sbatch 001.submit_dock.sh

It can also be run in serial by commenting out parallel lines and uncommenting bottom section
   bash 001.submit_dock.sh

   bash 002.index_lowest_scr.sh

Then openbabel is contingency for next step, but other conversion programs, such as chimera can potentially work:
   bash 003.pdbqt_to_mol2.sh

Then the pose RMSD is calculated via DOCK6
   bash 004.dock6_RMSDh.sh

Then calculate success, scoring fail and sample fail
   bash 005.calc_outcome.sh 
